sequenceDiagram
    actor F as Fran
    participant A as Advisor
    participant C as Contract
    participant R as Route
    participant U as Game UI
    C->>R: Handshake pins contract
    R->>R: Enter Preparing and reconcile
    alt Preflight fails
        R-->>F: Pause before travel or purchase
    else Preflight succeeds
        R->>U: Inspect exact visible row
        U-->>R: Current UI evidence
        alt Row satisfies contract
            R->>U: Purchase and verify
        else Approved policy permits recovery
            R->>R: Replan within policy version
            R->>U: Revalidate replacement and purchase
        else Recovery is not authorized
            R-->>F: Pause with changed-plan diff
        else Gear identity must change
            R-->>A: Return purchases and evidence
            A-->>F: Show revised frontier
        end
        R->>R: Record sunk quantity and gil
    end
    Note over R,U: M8.5 owns post-handshake behavior
